Description:
    Creates a new "basic" (HTML-only) meteor widget.  Not a fancy crud widget, just a HTML widget.

Example:
    ./script/generate meteor_widget hello_world

    This will create:
      dir  lib/meteor/widget/hello_world
      file lib/meteor/widget/hello_world/spec.rb
      dir  app/views/meteor/hello_world
      file app/views/meteor/hello_world/_render.rhtml      
